Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.73,0:24:34.99,Narration,,0,0,0,,Jananda, island of the lawless.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:32.76,00:24:35.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,（観察者）無法の島 ジャナンダ島
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.04,0:24:40.66,Narration,,0,0,0,,An island where prisoners kill each \Nother to have their wishes granted.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:37.05,00:24:41.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,囚人が望みをかなえるために\N殺し合う島
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.67,0:24:46.91,Narration,,0,0,0,,Fushi, being immortal, came to \Nbe the hope of five children.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:42.77,00:24:47.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,不死身のフシは\N５人の子供たちの希望となった
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.88,0:24:53.14,Narration,,0,0,0,,Fushi has yet to notice the footsteps \Napproaching from the past.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:48.94,00:24:54.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,過去から忍び寄る足音に\Nフシは まだ気づかない
